{"id": "anc_orbit", "modality": "animations", "name": "Orbit", "task": {"description": "Create a self-contained 1920x1080 HTML animation (inline CSS/SVG, NO <canvas>) of SIX equal-size dots orbiting a centered label at a FIXED radius, evenly spaced around the circle (60 degrees apart). Over ~4s they rotate together about the center (at least a quarter turn) while staying evenly spaced on the circle. The center label stays fixed.", "requirements": ["Exactly 6 equal-size dots are evenly spaced (about 60 degrees apart) on a circle at every frame", "All 6 dots stay fully within the viewport at every frame (none drifts off the circle or off-canvas)", "The dots' angular positions change over time (they orbit)", "The dots maintain a constant radius from the center (they stay on the circle, not spiraling)", "No dot overlaps the center label", "The center label stays fixed at the center throughout"], "difficulty": "hard"}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 1864, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 1682}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 1686, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 1672}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 1689, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 1689}], "ss_img": "images/animations/anc_orbit_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/animations/anc_orbit_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Orbital Animation</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #16213e);\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .orbit-container {\n            position: relative;\n            width: 600px;\n            height: 600px;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        .center-label {\n            position: absolute;\n            z-index: 10;\n            background: #ffffff;\n            color: #1a1a2e;\n            padding: 24px 48px;\n            border-radius: 50px;\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n            border: 3px solid #4a90e2;\n        }\n\n        .orbit-ring {\n            position: absolute;\n            width: 500px;\n            height: 500px;\n            border: 2px solid rgba(74, 144, 226, 0.2);\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            animation: rotate 4s linear infinite;\n        }\n\n        .dot {\n            position: absolute;\n            width: 40px;\n            height: 40px;\n            background: #4a90e2;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            top: 50%;\n            left: 50%;\n            transform-origin: 0 0;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(74, 144, 226, 0.4);\n            border: 3px solid #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        .dot::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            width: 20px;\n            height: 20px;\n            background: #ffffff;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            top: 50%;\n            left: 50%;\n            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);\n        }\n\n        /* Position each dot at 60-degree intervals around the circle */\n        .dot:nth-child(1) {\n            transform: translate(-20px, -20px) rotate(0deg) translateX(250px);\n        }\n\n        .dot:nth-child(2) {\n            transform: translate(-20px, -20px) rotate(60deg) translateX(250px);\n        }\n\n        .dot:nth-child(3) {\n            transform: translate(-20px, -20px) rotate(120deg) translateX(250px);\n        }\n\n        .dot:nth-child(4) {\n            transform: translate(-20px, -20px) rotate(180deg) translateX(250px);\n        }\n\n        .dot:nth-child(5) {\n            transform: translate(-20px, -20px) rotate(240deg) translateX(250px);\n        }\n\n        .dot:nth-child(6) {\n            transform: translate(-20px, -20px) rotate(300deg) translateX(250px);\n        }\n\n        @keyframes rotate {\n            from {\n                transform: rotate(0deg);\n            }\n            to {\n                transform: rotate(360deg);\n            }\n        }\n\n        /* Subtle pulsing animation for the center label */\n        .center-label {\n            animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite alternate;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes pulse {\n            from {\n                box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n            }\n            to {\n                box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(74, 144, 226, 0.4);\n            }\n        }\n\n        /* Add a subtle glow effect to dots */\n        .dot {\n            animation: rotate 4s linear infinite, glow 2s ease-in-out infinite alternate;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes glow {\n            from {\n                box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(74, 144, 226, 0.4);\n            }\n            to {\n                box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(74, 144, 226, 0.6);\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"orbit-container\">\n        <div class=\"center-label\">CENTER</div>\n        <div class=\"orbit-ring\">\n            <div class=\"dot\"></div>\n            <div class=\"dot\"></div>\n            <div class=\"dot\"></div>\n            <div class=\"dot\"></div>\n            <div class=\"dot\"></div>\n            <div class=\"dot\"></div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>", "rv_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Orbital Animation</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #16213e);\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .orbit-container {\n            position: relative;\n            width: 600px;\n            height: 600px;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        .center-label {\n            position: absolute;\n            z-index: 10;\n            background: #ffffff;\n            color: #1a1a2e;\n            padding: 24px 48px;\n            border-radius: 50px;\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n            border: 3px solid #4a90e2;\n        }\n\n        .orbit-ring {\n            position: absolute;\n            width: 500px;\n            height: 500px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            animation: rotate 4s linear infinite;\n        }\n\n        .dot {\n            position: absolute;\n            width: 40px;\n            height: 40px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            background: #4a90e2;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(74, 144, 226, 0.4);\n            border: 3px solid #ffffff;\n            top: 50%;\n            left: 50%;\n            transform-origin: 0 0;\n        }\n\n        .dot:nth-child(1) {\n            transform: translate(-20px, -20px) translate(250px, 0) rotate(0deg);\n            background: #4a90e2;\n        }\n\n        .dot:nth-child(2) {\n            transform: translate(-20px, -20px) translate(216.5px, 125px) rotate(60deg);\n            background: #5cb85c;\n        }\n\n        .dot:nth-child(3) {\n            transform: translate(-20px, -20px) translate(33.5px, 125px) rotate(120deg);\n            background: #f0ad4e;\n        }\n\n        .dot:nth-child(4) {\n            transform: translate(-20px, -20px) translate(-250px, 0) rotate(180deg);\n            background: #d9534f;\n        }\n\n        .dot:nth-child(5) {\n            transform: translate(-20px, -20px) translate(-216.5px, -125px) rotate(240deg);\n            background: #9b59b6;\n        }\n\n        .dot:nth-child(6) {\n            transform: translate(-20px, -20px) translate(33.5px, -125px) rotate(300deg);\n            background: #e67e22;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes rotate {\n            from {\n                transform: rotate(0deg);\n            }\n            to {\n                transform: rotate(360deg);\n            }\n        }\n\n        .orbit-ring::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 50%;\n            left: 50%;\n            width: 500px;\n            height: 500px;\n            border: 2px dashed rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"orbit-container\">\n        <div class=\"center-label\">CENTER</div>\n        <div class=\"orbit-ring\">\n            <div class=\"dot\"></div>\n            <div class=\"dot\"></div>\n            <div class=\"dot\"></div>\n            <div class=\"dot\"></div>\n            <div class=\"dot\"></div>\n            <div class=\"dot\"></div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>"}